name: Wild Flowers / Canon 17 & Helios 40
description:
Wild flowers on a sunny day.

Shot with the Canon 17mm F4 lens & Helios 40 85mm F1.5 Russian lens.
Part of a series of works exploring odd/cult/vintage lenses on modern digital cameras.

1 min 1920x1080 (100fps slow motion)
